Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mistral Wind！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:00:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Words Worth (光與影的傳說)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光與影再次分隔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟著過了20年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是普陸斯大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑了！普陸斯大人笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的！笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是普陸斯大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三話  [ 傳說中的劍士 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記不起 我…是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很美…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的劍術…原來這麼厲害的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳…妳有受傷嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不方便…請你不要再走近…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還未向他道謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這種骯髒的流浪客來的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快給我滾！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:04:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想跟我們打嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我不是那意思…只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把那隻兇猛的熊一刀兩斷？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 簡直好像閃電時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一道光劃破天際一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美茹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳還是不要一個人去那個森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺 你又跟媽媽說同一番話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪莉亞也那樣說？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 但是 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我不趁現在體驗多一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我長大後便會活得很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我說不過妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手！你們做甚麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙真無用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺！就是那個人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛兵們！聽令！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法布利陛下呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺死那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我一口氣宰掉他！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是法布利陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是法布利國王的命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺死他！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做甚麼！？爺爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我的救命恩人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 原來你失憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 你的樣貌和身形…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都跟人稱光之一族最強的劍士…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊 在你恢復記憶之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就以光之劍士普陸斯的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在這座城堡裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為怎說也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都是我的孫女美茹的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳看妳看 媽媽 很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要快點了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次又麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有錯 這是 Words Worth 石板的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禾斯卡陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們…光之一族會再次來襲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會 他們一定會再來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來奪取這塊 Words Worth 石板的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 經過那場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光與影兩國之間的通路…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給堵塞了20年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們一直毫無動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Words Worth 石板再過不久便會回服原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？達西奧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒甚麼…禾斯卡陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多年的心願終於能達成了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾殿下在九泉之下…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定會很高興的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾他…！不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾殿下還未肯定是死了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種口吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎朗 夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 大家聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要準備周全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防他們隨時來襲 知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悶死人了 沒有有趣的事情發生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要快點了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Words Worth 石板會復原過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,達西奧那傢伙幹嗎這麼匆忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難…難道曼查那傢伙…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那道光是甚麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:12:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才無人看見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來做甚麼？曼查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的招呼很無禮貌吧 拍檔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枉我這麼辛苦來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連我也覺得很嘔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 總算不用我主動去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 你有甚麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒事 我會特意走來嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也說得是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則光與影兩國的參謀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎會悄悄地見面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人會料到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光之國的參謀？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次真是謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽爺爺說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他派你去鄰近的礦山尋找…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光與影兩國之間的通路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及 Words Worth 石板的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我在森林找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是石板的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有相同的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳看 就是這塊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯大人！你從哪裡得來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 我一直帶在身的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定自從失憶前便帶著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:13:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼事！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是甚麼回事！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無效
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:14:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來解決牠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕…世上竟然有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不知道的可怕生物…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你！請你令我不再顫抖！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美茹…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你抱著我…讓我忘掉這種恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美茹小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？曼查！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我派去查探石板碎片的分身…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來給人消滅了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼！？究竟是甚麼人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信…是他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是來跟你談那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說中的劍士嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要快點收拾他！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯大人…！很難為情的…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美茹小姐 妳很美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…別那樣子望著我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體熱起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯大人…我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳對我一無所知 可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普陸斯大人…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？裡面有些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是水晶鎖匙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是媽媽叫我交給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那應該一定幫到你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你一定要回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說中的劍士普陸斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要設法消滅他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禾斯卡也找到正暗中復原的石板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不再次破壞它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們便無處容身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次破壞 Words Worth 石板？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們究竟…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來不妙 還是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曼查
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一座就是據稱…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏有光與影之間的通路的山嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水晶鎖匙發光！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風景真美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們想做甚麼！？怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳沒資格稱我們為怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖的別掙扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳很快便會成為我們的僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會…！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會爆發戰爭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.58,0:23:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何那樣問？亞利杜妮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.25,0:23:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大班劍士…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.75,0:23:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大清早便去到城堡集合
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.09,0:23:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.01,0:23:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又會爆發戰爭？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:23:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾斯托爾殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？那個姐姐有點不妥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.94,0:24:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.19,0:24:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳沒事吧？姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.70,0:24:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚麼也記不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.29,0:24:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼也記不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.96,0:24:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐！危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.13,0:24:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光與影結合的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.22,0:24:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐飛走了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.98,0:24:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像說了些甚麼 但她很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.32,0:24:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好極
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.16,0:24:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那對母女…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.83,0:25:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.00,0:25:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給20年前的戰爭堵塞了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.25,0:25:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光與影兩國之間的通路的…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山洞入口嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.03,0:25:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.21,0:25:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通路給堵塞了 就是這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.80,0:25:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水晶鎖匙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.14,0:26:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.57,0:26:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才好像美茹的女人是甚麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.74,0:26:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的過去究竟…？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.83,0:26:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.60,0:26:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Words Worth (光與影的傳說) 第三話完  待續
